Heat Transfer

Inputs
- Lounge temperature
- Bedroom temperatures
- Time of day

Outputs
- Relay
- Bedroom 1 PWM
- Bedroom 2 PWM
- Bedroom 3 PWM

Algorithm
1. Determine lounge reference temperature.
2. Compare against bedrooms.
3. Enable/disable transfer.
4. Calculate PWM ratios.
5. Apply comfort overrides.
6. Apply total PWM limit.
7. Write outputs.
